Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: Mock data file not found

Solution: Verify you're in the correct directory (~/breach_analysis_lab) and that mock_data/sample_breach.json exists
Issue: Import errors for matplotlib or pandas

Solution: Reinstall packages: pip3 install --upgrade matplotlib pandas seaborn
Issue: JSON parsing errors

Solution: Validate JSON syntax using jq command: jq . mock_data/sample_breach.json
Issue: Permission denied when running scripts

Solution: Ensure scripts are executable: chmod +x *.py
Issue: Empty or incomplete analysis results

Solution: Check that query results file contains valid data before analysis
